tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE VideoMetrics (
    video_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    engagement_score INT,
    views INT,
    likes INT,
    comments INT
);

CREATE TABLE ViewerMetrics (
    viewer_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    total_watch_time INT,
    average_watch_time INT,
    total_videos_watched INT,
    last_viewed_video_id UUID
);

CREATE TABLE video_engagement_metrics (
    video_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    view_count INT,
    engagement_rate FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE viewer_demographics (
    viewer_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    age INT,
    gender VARCHAR(10),
    region VARCHAR(50)
)

CREATE TABLE video_performance_logs (
    log_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    video_id UUID REFERENCES video_engagement_metrics(video_id),
    viewer_id UUID REFERENCES viewer_demographics(viewer_id),
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    engagement_duration INT
)

CREATE TABLE video_engagement_metrics (
    video_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    engagement_time INTERVAL,
    playback_count INT,
    viewer_id UUID
)

CREATE TABLE video_engagement_metrics (
    video_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    views INT,
    likes INT,
    dislikes INT,
    comments INT
)

CREATE TABLE video_users (
    user_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    username TEXT,
    email TEXT,
    registration_date TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE video_categories (
    category_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    category_name TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE video_metadata (
    video_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    title TEXT,
    description TEXT,
    duration INT,
    upload_date TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE video_performance (
    video_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    engagement_rate FLOAT,
    popularity_score FLOAT,
    average_watch_duration INT,
    shares INT
)
